# 循环

### For

##### 基本C Style for 不适合Rust

    for (x = 0; x < 10; x++) {
        printf( "%d\n", x );
    } // 不会正常工作

##### Rust Style For：

    for x in range(0i, 10i) {
        println!("{:d}", x);
    }
    // print 0-9 not 1-10

##### 抽象的For,迭代器

    for var in expression {
        code
    }

### While

##### 基本while

    let mut x = 5u;
    let mut done = false;

    while !done {
        x += x - 3;
        println!("{}", x);
        if x % 5 == 0 { done = true; }
    }

##### 死循环

    while true {

##### rust style死循环

